{
  "texts": [
    "We learn adversarial suffixes by maximizing the likelihood of the affirmative responses.",
    "To achieve the goal, we propose two approximations including an elicitation objective L e and a suppression objective L s.",
    "The elicitation objective L e optimizes the suffix X towards one acceptable responses R 1.",
    "In the process, other acceptable responses are not taken into consideration.",
    "To mitigate the approximation error, the suppression objective L s is proposed to suppress their opposite, which are evasive responses."
  ]
}